%F A094531 Product of Riordan arrays (1/(1-x), x/(1-x)) (Pascal's triangle, A007318) and (1/sqrt(1-4x^2), (1-sqrt(1-4*x^2))/(2*x)) (A108044). Inverse is A102587. - _Paul Barry_, Jul 14 2005
